name: Family Over Everything
description: Family Over Everything (FOE) is more than just a token - it's a supportive community that allows its family members to grow their assets collectively. We are real people, and we support our family members in their daily lives, through givebacks and financial support that goes beyond just discounts. We want to build a community based on mutual support and shared prosperity, and we're dedicated to helping our token holders achieve financial security. Limitless use cases for merchants and brands. The FOE token presents a unique opportunity for merchants and brands to deliver real value for their customers, while helping to fuel the FOE economy.
